  "page": "Torrhen",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Torrhen</b> is a northern given name.\n</p><p>It may refer to the following characters:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Torrhen_Karstark\" title=\"Torrhen Karstark\">Torrhen Karstark</a>, youngest son of Lord Rickard Karstark</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Torrhen_Manderly\" title=\"Torrhen Manderly\">Torrhen Manderly</a>, Lord Regent and Hand of the King during the minority of King Aegon III Targaryen</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Torrhen_Stark\" title=\"Torrhen Stark\">Torrhen Stark</a>, known as the \"King Who Knelt\", last King in the North</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Torrhen_Stark_(son_of_Edric)\" title=\"Torrhen Stark (son of Edric)\">Torrhen Stark</a>, younger son of Serena and Edric Stark, twin to Cregard Stark</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Torrhen_Whitehill\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Torrhen Whitehill\">Torrhen Whitehill</a>, a character created for the video game <i>Game of Thrones - A Telltale Games Series</i></li></ul>\n<p>Additionally, <b>Torrhen</b> may refer to:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Torrhen%27s_Square\" title=\"Torrhen&#39;s Square\">Torrhen's Square</a>, a castle in the north and the seat of House Tallhart</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Torrhen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Torren_Liddle\" title=\"Torren Liddle\">Torren Liddle</a>, the head of House Liddle</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405082847\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.003 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.004 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8/1000000\